Class LastMoveQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • production.DanChunn.util.LastMoveQueue

  • public class LastMoveQueue
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a class that is a modified version of a queue, built off of Array Lists It is used for saving and loading game files Created by willsuchanek on 4/3/17.
